BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:mksDoSJsdYdskdeYDRZXU
SUMMARY:Solidarity Dinner: South Seattle
DTSTAMP:20260409T031212Z
DTSTART:20260523T163000Z
DESCRIPTION:Dinner for the people! \\nHelp us cook\\\, serve\\\, eat togeth
	er\\\, and connect with our neighbors. \\nWe feed our community\\\, no que
	stions asked\\\, because we believe in our world where no one goes hungry.
	 \\nSaturdays in South Seattle:\\n-Cooking shift: 1:30-4pm in Tukwila\\n-S
	erving shift: 4:30-7pm at Cafe Red (across the street from the light rail 
	station) \\nTo volunteer for a cooking or serving shift\\\, follow the ins
	tructions here. \\nWe are also looking for financial supporters. It costs 
	just $2 to feed a hungry neighbor. Support here!\n\nhttps://seattledsa.org
	/event/solidarity-dinner-south-seattle/2026-05-23/\n\nFrom Seattle DSA
URL:https://seattledsa.org/event/solidarity-dinner-south-seattle/2026-05-23
	/
LOCATION:Cafe Red\\\, 7148 Martin Luther King Jr Way S\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\
	\, 98118\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seattle-dsa
CATEGORIES:Seattle DSA
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:MPRCsgeHTqiqqb7BB45XC
SUMMARY:Socialist Soccer! 2pm - 4pm
DTSTAMP:20260409T031212Z
DTSTART:20260524T140000Z
DESCRIPTION:Come play soccer with fellow socialists! This is a fun\\\, enjo
	yable way to get outdoors\\\, exercise\\\, and meet friendly socialists as
	 well as non-socialist soccer enthusiasts! \\nAll genders and skill levels
	 are welcome! Safety is our top priority. To participate you must abide by
	 our norms and agreements to avoid injuries and help us take care of one a
	nother. \\nJoin us at Brighton Playfield in South Seattle. Map: goo.gl/map
	s/c74cytjrRB1vpT7h7\\nWe almost always play on the most southern edge of t
	he field. \\nWe confirm if we have enough players each Sunday on a sociali
	st soccer Signal chat. To be added\\\, download the Signal app\\\, and ema
	il your phone number to tdupuis42@gmail.com with a request to be added. \\
	nThe game is usually at 10 AM\\\, but that may change\\\, so make sure you
	 are on the Socialist Soccer signal chat!\n\nhttps://seattledsa.org/event/
	socialist-soccer-2pm-4pm/2026-05-24/\n\nFrom Seattle DSA
URL:https://seattledsa.org/event/socialist-soccer-2pm-4pm/2026-05-24/
LOCATION:Brighton Playfield\\\, 6000 39th Ave S\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 9811
	8\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seattle-dsa
CATEGORIES:Seattle DSA
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
