	 Group! Free food and drinks will be provided. \\nThe Housing Justice Work
	ing Group is committed to creating a Seattle without sweeps\\\, evictions\
	\\, or housing scarcity\\\, where housing is a human right and not a commo
	dity. \\nThe full agenda is available on Discord (check out the pinned com
	ment in the housing-justice-general channel). If you aren’t part of the Di
	scord yet\\\, members in good standing can join here.\n\nhttps://seattleds
	a.org/event/housing-biweekly-meeting-13/\n\nFrom Seattle DSA
